short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Manage tabs in a vertical layout!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Work with tabs the way they were meant to be.

* Find your tabs easier
* Escape the limitations of a tab bar
* Minimal design to keep you focused

Use the keyboard shortcut to quickly open dot tabs
- Cmd + E (Mac)
- Ctrl + E (Windows, ChromeOS, Linux)
